cials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20Harvard%20has%20to%20do%20is%20honor%20the%20agreement%20it%20had%20made%20with%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Ackman%20wrote%20Tuesday.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%2C%20to%20grant%20me%20the%20right%20I%20bargained%20for%3A%20The%20right%20to%20allocate%20the%20%2470m%20of%20excess%20proceeds%20to%20the%20Harvard-related%20initiative%20of%20my%20choice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharvard-missed-out-75-million-potential-gains-bill-ackman-says-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702433878000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65790ad17a3c8094d5dc5846%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharvard-missed-out-75-million-potential-gains-bill-ackman-says-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bill%20Ackman%20rejected%20the%20narrative%20that%20his%20crusade%20against%20Harvard%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20has%20been%20fueled%20by%20personal%20resentment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22esnodgrass%40insider.com%20(Erin%20Snodgrass)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharvard-missed-out-75-million-potential-gains-bill-ackman-says-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Google's%20Court%20Defeat%20To%20Fortnite%20Maker%20May%20Spell%20Trouble%20For%20Big%20Tech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGoogle'%20stinging%20defeat%20against%20Fortnite-maker%20Epic%20Games%20in%20a%20California%20courtroom%20could%20be%20an%20important%20blow%20against%20big%20tech's%20decades%20of%20supremacy%20on%20antitrust%20matters%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Washington%20lawmaking%20gridlocked%20and%20pro-business%20judges%20dominant%20in%20federal%20courts%2C%20US%20tech%20giants%20have%20survived%20unscathed%20for%20years%20against%20accusations%20of%20wielding%20illegal%20monopoly%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Europe%2C%20Britain%2C%20India%20and%20others%20enforce%20regulations%20that%20at%20least%20try%20to%20keep%20big%20tech%20in%20check%2C%20Google%2C%20Apple%2C%20Meta%20and%20Amazon%20have%20yet%20to%20suffer%20a%20significant%20setback%20on%20their%20home%20turf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20jury%20of%20nine%20on%20Monday%20possibly%20changed%20that%20equation%2C%20setting%20an%20important%20precedent%20that%20could%20send%20tremors%20in%20other%20cases%20pending%20against%20the%20tech%20giants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBig%20tech%20is%20not%20above%20the%20law.%20This%20loss%20isn't%20just%20the%20first%20antitrust%20failure%20for%20Google%2C%20it's%20the%20first%20antitrust%20loss%20for%20any%20big%20tech%20firm%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Matt%20Stoller%2C%20director%20of%20research%20at%20the%20American%20Economic%20Liberties%20Project%20and%20a%20critic%20of%20big%20tech%20business%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20jury%20in%20San%20Francisco%20took%20just%20three%20hours%20on%20Monday%20to%20decide%20that%20Epic%20Games%20was%20slighted%20by%20Google's%20refusal%20to%20let%20outside%20apps%20take%20payments%20on%20Android%20phones%2C%20other%20than%20through%20the%20search%20giant's%20app%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Greedy%20behemoth'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20three%20year%20battle%2C%20Epic%20Games%20was%20finally%20vindicated%20after%20seeming%20to%20be%20on%20the%20backfoot%20when%20a%20different%20judge%20largely%20decided%20against%20the%20video%20game%20maker%20in%20a%20case%20involving%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Epic's%20CEO%20Tim%20Sweeney%20refused%20to%20back%20down%20and%20when%20other%20developers%20settled%20with%20Google%2C%20he%20stuck%20to%20his%20guns%2C%20repeating%20his%20demand%20that%20Google%20open%20up%20Android%20smartphones%20to%20other%20modes%20of%20payment%2C%20and%20without%20charging%20a%20hefty%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohn%20Lopatka%2C%20from%20Penn%20State%20University'%20law%20school%2C%20said%20it%20was%20predictable%20that%20juries%20side%20with%20plaintiffs%20in%20monopoly%20cases%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20the%20defendant%20will%20be%20painted%20as%20a%20greedy%20behemoth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple's%20case%2C%20decided%20by%20a%20judge%2C%20avoided%20that%20fate%20--%20but%20not%20so%20for%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20two%20questions%20remain%3A%20what%20will%20happen%20on%20Google's%20appeal%2C%20and%20how%20will%20the%20judge%20order%20Google%20to%20fulfill%20the%20jury's%20decision%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20litigation%20%26quot%3Bhas%20some%20distance%20to%20go%20before%20we%20know%20the%20final%20resolution%2C%26quot%3B%20warned%20Lopatka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appeals%20court%20that%20will%20likely%20hear%20the%20Google%20case%20is%20the%20same%20one%20that%20largely%20dismissed%20Epic's%20appeal%20against%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%26quot%3Bappellate%20courts%20do%20not%20set%20aside%20jury%20verdicts%20and%20remedial%20orders%20lightly%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lopatka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remedy%20could%20very%20likely%20have%20a%20huge%20impact%2C%20with%20Apple's%20behavior%20regarding%20its%20own%20app%20store%20potentially%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEpic%20very%20clearly%20wants%20the%20judge%20%26quot%3Bto%20mandate%20alternative%20app%20stores%20and%20alternate%20billing%20systems%20on%20Android%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Adam%20Kovacevich%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20Chamber%20of%20Progress%2C%20a%20tech%20industry%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20would%20be%20a%20pretty%20sweeping%20remedy.%20It%20would%20certainly%20change%20Android%20as%20we%20know%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Changing%20the%20world'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBig%20tech's%20longtime%20critics%20point%20to%20Google's%20other%20major%20case%2C%20where%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20is%20suing%20Google%20over%20its%20online%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20case%20will%20be%20decided%20by%20a%20judge%20and%20not%20a%20jury%2C%20but%20Stoller%20said%20the%20Epic%20decision%20changes%20the%20dynamic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20judge%20there%20%26quot%3Bchooses%20to%20let%20Google%20off%20the%20hook%2C%20well%2C%20he'll%20look%20pretty%20bad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20cases%2C%20Apple%20looms%20large%20--%20and%20many%20wonder%20whether%20the%20iPhone%20maker%20will%20be%20able%20to%20avoid%20being%20dragged%20back%20to%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApple%20is%20next%20over%20the%20barrel%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Luther%20Lowe%2C%20head%20of%20public%20policy%20at%20Y%20Combinator%2C%20the%20startup%20hub.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECourt%20documents%20showed%20in%20both%20cases%20that%20Google%20made%20huge%20payments%20to%20smartphone%20makers%20to%20ensure%20that%20its%20products%20kept%20a%20predominant%20place%20on%20devices%2C%20crushing%20rivals%20before%20they%20can%20emerge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoogle%20and%20Apple%20both%20treat%20developers%20as%20adversaries%2C%26quot%3B%20Epic%20CEO%20Sweeney%20told%20The%20Verge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20do%20absolutely%20everything%20we%20can%2C%20as%20quickly%20as%20we%20can%2C%20to%20start%20changing%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702433820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fmg35f038_google-generic-file_625x300_20_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgoogles-court-defeat-to-fortnite-maker-may-spell-trouble-for-big-tech-4663920%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google'%20stinging%20defeat%20against%20Fortnite-maker%20E