%20that%20Mahadev%20Online%20Book%20App%20is%20run%20from%20a%20central%20head%20office%20in%20the%20UAE%2C%20officials%20said.%20It%20operates%20by%20franchising%20%26quot%3BPanel%2FBranches%26quot%3B%20to%20their%20known%20associates%20on%2070-30%20per%20cent%20profit%20ratio%2C%20it%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELarge%20scale%20hawala%20operations%20are%20done%20to%20siphon%20off%20the%20proceeds%20of%20betting%20to%20off-shore%20accounts%2C%20it%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELarge%20expenditure%20in%20cash%20is%20also%20being%20done%20in%20India%20for%20advertising%20of%20betting%20websites%20to%20attract%20new%20users%20and%20franchise%20(panel)%20seekers%2C%20the%20ED%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20promoters%20hail%20from%20Bhilai%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20the%20Mahadev%20online%20book%20betting%20application%20is%20an%20umbrella%20syndicate%20arranging%20online%20platforms%20for%20enabling%20illegal%20betting%20websites.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702433640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-12%2Fo95vbtc8_dubai-police-generic-twitter-650_625x300_09_December_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahadev-betting-app-owner-ravi-uppal-detained-in-dubai-4663918%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravi%20Uppal%2C%20one%20of%20the%20two%20main%20owners%20of%20the%20Mahadev%20online%20betting%20app%2C%20has%20been%20detained%20in%20Dubai%20by%20the%20local%20police%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20red%20notice%20issued%20by%20Interpol%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20ED%2C%20official%20sources%20said%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahadev-betting-app-owner-ravi-uppal-detained-in-dubai-4663918%22%2C%22c