d%20have%20been%20an%20immediate%2C%20direct%2C%20and%20unequivocal%20condemnation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20corporation%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCalls%20for%20genocide%20are%20despicable%20and%20contrary%20to%20fundamental%20human%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Gay%20has%20apologized%20for%20how%20she%20handled%20her%20congressional%20testimony.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERabbi%20Getzel%20Davis%2C%20a%20Harvard%20campus%20chaplain%20and%20member%20of%20the%20Hillel%20Jewish%20student%20movement%2C%20said%20in%20response%20to%20the%20corporation's%20announcement%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20important%20thing%20for%20Jewish%20students%20at%20Harvard%20and%20Harvard%20Hillel%20is%20that%20the%20culture%20changes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20look%20forward%20to%20continuing%20to%20work%20with%20President%20Gay%20and%20other%20senior%20Harvard%20administrators%20on...%20enforcing%20policies%20to%20protect%20Jewish%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUniversity%20of%20Pennsylvania's%20president%20Liz%20Magill%20resigned%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20her%20responses%20to%20Congress%2C%20and%20pressure%20had%20mounted%20on%20Gay%20both%20inside%20and%20outside%20of%20Harvard%20to%20follow%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2070%20lawmakers%20including%20two%20Democrats%20called%20for%20her%20resignation%2C%20while%20a%20number%20of%20high-profile%20Harvard%20alumni%20and%20donors%20have%20called%20for%20her%20departure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20excess%20of%20700%20Harvard%20faculty%20members%20signed%20a%20letter%20supporting%20Gay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGay%2C%2053%2C%20was%20born%20in%20New%20York%20to%20Haitian%20immigrants%20and%20is%20a%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20who%20in%20July%20became%20the%20first%20Black%20president%20of%20368-year-old%20Harvard%20University%2C%20in%20Cambridge%2C%20outside%20Boston.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERyan%20Enos%2C%20professor%20of%20government%20at%20Harvard%