0Are%20you%20the%20kind%20of%20couple%20that%20spends%2075%25%20of%20the%20time%20fighting%20and%2025%25%20having%20fun%3F%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20so%2C%20she%20said%20that%20doesn't%20bode%20well%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsigns-youre-in-a-healthy-relationship-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehappy%2C%20long-term%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20You%20hold%20back%20parts%20of%20yourself%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20said%20that%20not%20everyone%20is%20comfortable%20with%20opening%20up%2C%20and%20that's%20ok.%20Some%20people%20are%20just%20naturally%20more%20extroverted%20than%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there's%20a%20difference%20between%20being%20naturally%20reserved%20and%20consciously%20holding%20back%20details%20about%20your%20life%2C%20whether%20it's%20your%20ambitions%20or%20parts%20of%20your%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20probably%20have%20a%20little%20voice%20inside%20our%20head%20saying%2C%20'I%20don't%20really%20want%20to%20share%20more%20with%20this%20person%2C'%26quot%3B%20South%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frelationships-that-last-share-these-qualities-2018-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elasting%20partnership%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20built%20on%20trust%20and%20the%20feeling%20that%20your%20partner%20is%20here%20to%20help%20you%20reach%20your%20goals.%20If%20you're%20hesitant%20about%20being%20your%20full%20self%20around%20your%20partner%2C%20it%20could%20mean%20that%20you%20don't%20think%20they'd%20have%20your%20back%20if%20you%20were%20authentic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20You%20keep%20wanting%20to%20change%20your%20partner%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20South%20said%20some%20people%20accept%20each%20other's%20differences%20early%20on%20or%20break%20up%2C%20there%20are%20also%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20who%20commit%20to%20a%20relationship%20and%20they%20feel%20like%20can%20get%20past%20whatever%20differences%20they%20have%20with%20this%20person.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20as%20the%20years%20pass%2C%20they're%20disappointed%20when%20they%20can't%20get%20past%20these%20differences%20%E2%80%94%20or%20that%20their%20partner%20can't%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20though%20some%20people%20do%20people%20change%20over%20time%2C%20most%20generally%20stay%20the%20same.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20you're%20in%20a%20long-term%20relationship%20and%20continually%20trying%20to%20tweak%20your%20partner%20into%20being%20the%20person%20you%20want%20them%20to%20be%2C%20it's%20a%20likely%20sign%20the%20relationship%20just%20isn't%20a%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20One%20or%20both%20of%20you%20changed%20and%20grew%20apart%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20one%20or%20both%20people%20can%20drastically%20change%2C%20according%20to%20South.%20One%20person%20might%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fdidnt-want-kids-relationship-changed-my-mind-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echange%20their%20mind%20on%20having%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20go%20through%20a%20mental%20health%20problem.%20Or%20they%20might%20just%20realize%20they%20want%20completely%20different%20things%20in%20life.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20wondering%20about%20why%20you%20feel%20confused%20about%20your%20relationship%2C%20South%20said%20a%20good%20question%20to%20ask%20is%20%26quot%3BHas%20the%20person%20changed%20in%20some%20way%2C%20or%20have%20you%20changed%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20you%20do%20next%20will%20vary%20based%20on%20what%20the%20changes%20are%20and%20how%20comfortable%20either%20of%20you%20is%20with%20adjusting.%20It%20can%20be%20a%20twist%20in%20a%20long%20life%20together%2C%20or%20a%20sign%20that%20your%20paths%20should%20split%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-youre-in-the-wrong-relationship-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702422722000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6577809158e7c0c29a2bdc84%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-youre-in-the-wrong-relationship-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Even%20if%20it%20feels%20right%2C%20there%20might%20be%20signs%20you%20are%20in%20the%20wrong%20relationship.%20According%20to%20a%20psychologist%2C%20fighting%20too%20often%20can%20mean%20you're%20incompatible.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpugachevsky%40insider.com%20(Julia%20Pugachevsky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-youre-in-the-wrong-relationship-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20UN%2C%20India%20Votes%20In%20Favour%20Of%20Resolution%20Demanding%20Gaza%20Ceasefire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%20has%20adopted%20a%20resolution%20'Protection%20of%20civilians%20and%20upholding%20legal%20and%20humanitarian%20obligations'%20demanding%20an%20immediate%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20ceasefire%20resolution%20in%20the%20UNGA's%20emergency%20session%20on%20the%20Middle%20East%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%20153%20nations%2C%20including%20India%2C%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20resolution%2C%20while%2010%2C%20including%20US%2C%20Israel%20and%20Austria%2C%20voted%20against%20and%2023%20countries%2C%20including%20Argentina%2C%20Ukraine%20and%20Germany%20abstained%20from%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20demands%20an%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20immediate%20and%20unconditional%20release%20of%20all%20hostages%20and%20well%20as%20%26quot%3Bensuring%20humanitarian%20access.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20demands%20that%20all%20parties%20comply%20with%20their%20obligations%20under%20international%20law%2C%20including%20humanitarian%20law%2C%20with%20regard%20to%20protection%20of%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Permanent%20Representative%20to%20the%20UN%2C%20Ruchira%20Kamboj%2C%20said%20that%20a%20terrorist%20attack%20occurred%20in%20Israel%20on%20October%207.%20She%20noted%20that%20there%20is%20an%20enormous%20humanitarian%20crisis%20and%20a%20large-scale%20loss%20of%20human%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20resolution%20just%20adopted%20by%20the%20General%20Assembly.%20The%20situation%20that%20this%20August%20body%20has%20been%20deliberating%20upon%20has%20many%20dimensions.%20There%20is%20the%20terrorist%20attack%20in%20Israel%20on%207%20October%20and%20the%20concern%20for%20the%20hostages%20taken%20at%20that%20time.%20There%20is%20an%20enormous%20humanitarian%20crisis%20and%20a%20large-scale%20loss%20of%20civilian%20lives%2C%20especially%20of%20women%20and%20children.There%20is%20the%20issue%20of%20observing%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20in%20all%20circumstances.%20And%20there%20is%20the%20endeavour%20to%20find%20a%20peaceful%20and%20lasting%20two-state%20solution%20to%20the%20longstanding%20Palestine%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Kamboj%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20India%20welcomes%20the%20unity%20of%20international%20community%20in%20finding%20a%20common%20ground%20the%20address%20the%20multiple%20challenges%20faced%20by%20the%20region%20at%20the%20present%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERuchira%20Kamboj%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20challenge%2C%20in%20this%20extraordinarily%20difficult%20time%2C%20is%20to%20strike%20the%20right%20balance.%20The%20gravity%20and%20complexity%20of%20what%20the%20international%20community%20faces%20are%20underlined%20by%20the%20secretary%20general%20invoking%20Article%2099%20of%20the%20Charter%20of%20the%20United%20Nations.%20We%2C%20therefore%2C%20welcome%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20international%20community%20unity%20has%20been%20able%20to%20find%20a%20common%20ground%20to%20address%20the%20multiple%20challenges%20facing%20the%20region%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20United%20States-led%20amendment%20to%20the%20draft%20resolution%20was%20not%20passed%20at%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly.%20As%20many%20as%2084%20nations%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20amendment%3B%2062%20voted%20against%20while%2025%20voted%20abstained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20Austria-led%20amendment%20to%20the%20draft%20resolution%20on%20the%20Gaza%20crisis%20failed%20to%20pass%20at%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly.%2089%20nations%20have%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20amendment%2C%2061%20voted%20against%20the%20amendment%20and%2020%20abstained%20from%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20Permanent%20Representative%2C%20Gilad%20Erdan%2C%20said%20that%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20finds%20itself%20%26quot%3Babout%20to%20vote%20on%20another%20hypocritical%20resolution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNot%20only%20does%20this%20resolution%20fail%20to%20condemn%20Hamas%20for%20crimes%20against%20humanity%2C%20it%20does%20not%20mention%20Hamas%20at%20all.%20This%20will%20only%20prolong%20the%20death%20and%20destruction%20in%20the%20region%2C%20that%20is%20precisely%20what%20a%20ceasefire%20means.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EErdan%20said%20that%20Hamas'%20only%20intention%20is%20to%20destroy%20Israel%20and%20the%20group%20has%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20repeat%20its%20atrocities%20again%20and%20again%20until%20Israel%20ceases%20to%20exist.%20He%20called%20for%20the%20need%20to%20hold%20Hamas%20accountable%20and%20added%20that%20a%20ceasefire%20means%20only%20one%20thing%20which%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bsurvival%20of%20Hamas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%20why%20would%20anyone%20want%20to%20aid%20Hamas%20in%20continuing%20their%20rule%20of%20terror%20and%20actualizing%20their%20satanic%20agenda%3F%26quot%3B%20He%20further%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20all%20know%20that%20the%20so%20call%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%20in%20this%20resolution%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20humanity.%20Israel%20is%20already%20taking%20every%20measure%20to%20facilitate%20the%20entry%20of%20humanitarian%20aid%20into%20Gaza.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMunir%20Akram%2C%20Pakistan's%20Permanent%20Representative%20to%20the%20UN%2C%20said%20it%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20regret%2C%20that%20some%20friends%20of%20Israel%20have%20introduced%20amendments%20to%20once%20again%20condemn%20only%20one%20side%20but%20exonerate%20the%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20war%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIsrael's%20goal%20is%20to%20erase%20not%20only%20a%20people%20but%20the%20entire%20idea%20of%20Palestine.%20It's%20campaign%20is%20a%20carbon%20copy%20of%20the%20massive%20campaigns%20of%20racial%20slaughter%20by%20other%20settler%20colonial%20regimes%20in%20history.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vote%20comes%20as%20the%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20enters%20its%20third%20month%2C%20with%20medics%20and%20aid%20groups%20expressing%20concern%20over%20the%20humanitarian%20situation%20in%20Gaza.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Israel%20has%20said%20it%20will%20not%20stop%20its%20military%20campaign%20until%20it%20destroys%20Hamas.%20Israel%20launched%20a%20counter-offensive%20against%20Hamas'%20after%20its%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702422600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fq85i0t2_gaza_625x300_12_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.