th%20the%20polish%20of%20a%20dress%20shirt%3F%20It's%20a%20tricky%20formula%20to%20perfect%2C%20but%20Rhone%20gets%20it%20right%20with%20the%20aptly%20named%20Commuter%20Dress%20Shirt.%20It's%20ideal%20for%20staying%20cool%20and%20comfortable%20(yet%20refined)%20on%20the%20go%2C%20whether%20your%20plans%20take%20you%20through%20the%20city%20to%20a%20rooftop%20happy%20hour%20or%20across%20the%20country%20for%20a%20coastal%20wedding.%20Crucially%2C%20it's%20built%20with%204-way%20stretch%20and%20anti-odor%20technology.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20inclusive%20sizing%3Cp%3EPolished%20performance%20is%20the%20name%20of%20the%20game%20with%20Swet%20Tailor%2C%20which%20delivers%20a%20substantial%20range%20of%20size%20options%20and%20builds%20its%20shirts%20with%20bigger%20guys%20in%20mind.%20The%20shirt%20blends%20a%20tailored%20look%20with%20a%20cotton-spandex%20blend%20for%20crucial%20stretch%20and%20breathability.%20Better%20still%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20this%20shirt%20can%20be%20worn%20tucked%20or%20untucked%2C%20and%20any%20of%20the%20versatile%2C%20breezy%20color%20options%20should%20match%20other%20classic%20wardrobe%20colors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20white%20dress%20shirt%3Cp%3EThe%20white%20shirt%20is%20an%20undeniable%20staple%20in%20every%20man's%20closet%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20need%20to%20wear%20one%20of%20the%20best%20performance%20dress%20shirts%20more%20than%20once%20a%20week%20(or%20even%20once%20a%20month).%20Stantt%20infused%20its%20take%20on%20a%20timeless%20essential%20with%20wrinkle-resistant%20tech%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20it's%20available%20in%20neck%20and%20sleeve%20sizes%20helps%20you%20dial%20in%20your%20perfect%20fit.%20The%20spread%20collar%20works%20particularly%20well%20for%20wearing%20with%20a%20tie%2C%20and%20the%20white%20color%20is%20as%20reliable%20as%20it%20gets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20slim-fit%3Cp%3EA%20slim-fit%20dress%20shirt%20can%20add%20plenty%20of%20polish%20to%20your%20wardrobe%2C%20whether%20worn%20tucked%20in%20with%20the%20sleeves%20rolled%20up%20or%20paired%20with%20a%20well-fitting%20sweater%20or%20cardigan.%20Here%2C%20Ash%20%26amp%3B%20Erie%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20find%20your%20perfect%20fit%20by%20neck%20sizing%2C%20and%20two%20reliable%20colors%20deliver%20plenty%20of%20styling%20potential%20in%20any%20season.%20For%20good%20measure%2C%20the%20wrinkle-resistant%20cotton%20is%20an%20optimal%20touch%20for%20tailored%20occasions%20aplenty.%20These%20shirts%20are%20also%20ideal%20for%20shorter%20guys%20(5'8%26quot%3B%20and%20under).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20oxford%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20often%20you%20come%20across%20a%20dress%20shirt%20that%20can%20perform%20as%20readily%20out%20in%20the%20field%20as%20it%20can%20back%20at%20the%20office%20or%20at%20a%20rooftop%20happy%20hour%2C%20but%20Western%20Rise%20has%20somehow%20managed%20to%20do%20the%20impossible.%20The%20key%20is%20the%20use%20of%20moisture-wicking%2C%20anti-microbial%20merino%20wool.%20What%20really%20seals%20the%20deal%20in%20terms%20of%20wearability%20is%20the%20expertly%20designed%2C%20hidden%20Oxford%20buttondown%20collar%20%E2%80%93%20that%20makes%20this%20one%20of%20the%20best%20performance%20dress%20shirts%20you%20can%20actually%20wear%20with%20dark%20blue%20jeans%20as%20well%20as%20tailored%20wool%20trousers%20or%20stretch%20cargo%20chinos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20business%20casual%3Cp%3EOpt%20for%20a%20better%20kind%20of%20business%20casual%20by%20switching%20out%20your%20polo%20for%20a%20stretchy%20dress%20shirt%20in%20an%20eye-catching%20color.%20B.%20Draddy%20specializes%20in%20performance%20apparel%20suitable%20for%20the%20golf%20course%2C%20but%20this%20cotton-nylon%20stretch%20shirt%20is%20well-suited%20for%20a%20post-links%20dinner%20or%20drinks%20(and%20again%2C%20the%20office).%20Memory%20collar%20stays%20ensure%20your%20collar%20frames%20your%20face%2C%20rather%20than%20lays%20flat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20business%20formal%3Cp%3EFor%20formal%20affairs%20%E2%80%94%20everything%20from%20a%20black%20tie%20to%20an%20all-important%20business%20meeting%20%E2%80%94%20a%20dress%20shirt%20with%20a%20more%20dressy%20flair%20is%20more%20than%20acceptable.%20In%20fact%2C%20it's%20practically%20required%2C%20and%20Eton%20dress%20shirts%20rise%20to%20the%20occasion.%20The%20elastane-enhanced%20recycled%20yarn%20is%20plenty%20stretchy%2C%20but%20it's%20the%20cutaway%20collar%20that%20takes%20this%20performance-minded%20shirt%20to%20the%20next%20level.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20with%20pockets%3Cp%3ESome%20dress%20shirts%20are%20made%20for%20only%20the%20most%20buttoned-up%20offices%2C%20but%20others%20inject%20a%20touch%20of%20outdoor-ready%20performance%20into%20the%20mix.%20KUHL%20used%20an%20advanced%20polyester%20performance%20fabric%20featuring%20UPF%2B%20technology%20to%20nail%20the%20right%20balance%20of%20rugged%20and%20refined.%20Better%20still%20is%20the%20handy%20pocket%20to%20store%20small%20EDC%20essentials%20when%20the%20time%20comes%20to%20venture%20into%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20made-to-measure%3Cp%3EBuying%20one%20of%20the%20best%20performance%20dress%20shirts%20doesn't%20have%20to%20feel%20intimidating%20%E2%80%93%20it%20can%20be%20as%20easy%20as%20taking%20your%20measurements%20(a%20fairly%20simple%20process)%20and%20then%20selecting%20from%20a%20wide%20array%20of%20options%20via%20Woodies.%20The%20results%20are%20tailored%20to%20your%20liking%2C%20from%20the%20collar%20to%20the%20cuff%20design%2C%20and%20you%20can%20even%20add%20a%20monogram.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fperformance-dress-shirts%5C%22%3EInsider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702417206000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F646651dffb9a9d0018c914cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID