2C%20frizz-free%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20straightening%20brushes%20because%20it%20also%20benefits%20from%20iRed%20Beam%20technology%3A%20It%20has%20far-infrared%20strips%20along%20the%20base%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20delivery%20of%20heat%20into%20your%20hair%20for%20faster%20styling%20and%20to%20retain%20moisture%20for%20healthy-looking%20hair%20(making%20the%20tool%20an%20excellent%20choice%20for%20fine%20or%20damaged%20hair).%20It%20also%20comes%20with%20a%2060-minute%20automatic%20shut-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20to%20splurge%20on%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20a%20diehard%20Drybar%20fan%20for%20years%2C%20and%20next%20to%20the%20brand's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fdrybar-double-shot-blow-dryer-brush-review%5C%22%3Eblow%20dryer%20brush%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20its%20Brush%20Crush%20Heated%20Straightening%20Brush%20is%20a%20beloved%20tool%20in%20my%20styling%20arsenal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDecked%20out%20in%20Drybar's%20signature%20yellow%2C%20this%20two-in-one%20styler%20is%20sturdy%20and%20built%20to%20last.%20It's%20structured%20like%20a%20paddle%20brush%20and%20heats%20up%20like%20a%20flat%20iron%2C%20so%20you%20can%20simultaneously%20straighten%20and%20work%20through%20any%20knots.%20The%20design%20includes%20ionic%20technology%20that%20seals%20strands'%20cuticles%2C%20reducing%20frizz%20and%20amplifying%20hair's%20natural%20shine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brush%20also%20features%20adjustable%20heat%20settings%20and%20shuts%20off%20automatically%20after%2060%20minutes.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94%20Julia%20Guerra%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20budget%3Cp%3EThe%20Revlon%20One-Step%20Hair%20Straightening%20Brush%20mirrors%20the%20average%20flat%20iron%20in%20length.%20Its%20surface%20measures%204%20%C2%BD%20inches%20long%20and%20consists%20of%20multidimensional%20combs%20and%20bristles%20that%20glide%20through%20strands%20without%20a%20snag.%20Bedhead%20won't%20stand%20a%20chance%20against%20this%20heated%20detangler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20budget-friendly%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20straightening%20brushes%20because%20it%20features%2010%20variable%20heat%20settings%2C%20and%20with%20the%20combination%20of%20warmth%20and%20the%20surface's%20ceramic%20coating%2C%20even%20dull%20hair%20will%20see%20a%20vast%20improvement%20in%20shine.%20The%20inclusion%20of%20an%20ion%20generator%20results%20in%20smoother%2C%20glossier%20strands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20curly%20hair%3Cp%3ETaming%20wild%20curls%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fcelebrities-embrace-natural-hair-while-social-distancing-2020-4%5C%22%3Eif%20you%20so%20choose%3C%2Fa%3E)%20can%20be%20challenging%2C%20but%20the%20Enhanced%20Hair%20Straightener%20Brush%20from%20MicroPure%20makes%20the%20process%20less%20taxing.%20According%20to%20the%2010%2C000%2B%20reviews%20on%20Amazon%20alone%2C%20MiroPure's%20straightening%20brush%20significantly%20reduces%20the%20time%20it%20takes%20those%20with%20curly%20hair%20types%20to%20straighten%20their%20hair.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20tight%20curls%2Fcoils%2C%20and%20this%20brush%20straightened%20better%20than%20my%20very%20expensive%20flat%20iron%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20reviewer.%20%26quot%3BIt%20only%20took%2016%20mins%20to%20do%20half%20of%20my%20hair!!%20I%20have%20never%20straightened%20my%20hair%20so%20quickly!%26quot%3B%20added%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20MicroPure%20features%2016%20impressive%20heat%20settings%20that%20help%20every%20hair%20type%20get%20its%20ideal%20style.%20Still%2C%20the%20straightening%20brush%20is%20an%20especially%20great%20option%20for%20wavy%20and%20curly%20hair%20types%20as%20the%20high-density%20nano%20comb%20bristles%20efficiently%20work%20through%20coarse%20strands%2C%20and%20its%20double%20ionic%20generator%20seals%20the%20hair%20cuticles%2C%20resulting%20in%20smoother%2C%20more%20lustrous%20hair.%20Plus%2C%20less%20time%20styling%20means%20less%20heat%20exposure%2C%20so%20hair%20will%20look%20and%20feel%20silkier%2C%20not%20dry%20and%20sullen%2C%20by%20the%20time%20you're%20finished.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20frizz%3Cp%3EGot%20frizz%2C%20poof%2C%20and%20flyaways%3F%20InStyler's%20straightening%20brush%20is%20the%20first%20on%20the%20market%20to%20boast%20as%20many%20ions%20as%20a%20blow%20dryer.%20It's%20these%20same%20ionic%20bristles%20that%20add%20a%20layer%20of%2C%20what%20the%20brand%20describes%20as%2C%20%26quot%3Bsuperior%20de-frizzing.%26quot%3B%20That%2C%20plus%20the%20brush's%20ceramic%20plate%20design%20(there%20are%2065%20in%20total)%2C%20adds%20up%20to%20one%20of%20the%20best%20straightening%20brushes%20built%20to%20smooth%20the%20most%20undulated%20strands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20reducing%20frizz%2C%20reviewers%20say%20the%20Straight%20Up%20Max%20Ionic%20Hot%20Brush%20is%20as%20quick%20as%20it%20is%20efficient%20in%20deflating%20poofy%20hair.%20%26quot%3BThis%20brush%20made%20my%20hair%20smooth%20and%20straight%20with%20one%20pass!%26quot%3B%20one%20reviewer%20raved%2C%20while%20another%20noted%20it%20makes%20their%20mornings%20%26quot%3Bso%20much%20easier.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20fine%20and%20damaged%20hair%3Cp%3EHot%20tools%20can%20do%20a%20number%20on%20hair%20if%20you're%20not%20careful%20(or%20if%20you're%20not%20using%20the%20right%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-heat-protectant%5C%22%3Eheat%20protectant%20products%3C%2Fa%3E).%20If%20it%20feels%20like%20your%20strands%20are%20at%20the%20point%20of%20no%20return%2C%20there's%20good%20news%3A%20The%20TYMO%20Hair%20Straightener%20Brush%20lets%20you%20style%20your%20hair%20and%20heal%20it%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pink%20tool%20does%20more%20than%20look%20pretty%20on%20your%20vanity.%20The%20brush%20is%20designed%20with%20an%20ionic%20coating%20that%20releases%20millions%20of%20ions%20in%20tandem%20with%20heat%20to%20create%20a%20prote