0by%20tax%20authorities%20and%20an%20ensuing%20investigation%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20over%20alleged%20FDI%20violations%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20establishment%20of%20Collective%20Newsroom%20Private%20Limited%20ensures%20the%20BBC%20and%20Collective%20Newsroom%20can%20meet%20their%20shared%20commitment%20to%20Indian%20audiences%20and%20cover%20stories%20on%20India%20that%20matter%20to%20global%20audiences.%20It%20is%20in%20compliance%20with%20the%20Indian%20Foreign%20Direct%20Investment%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20the%20BBC%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCollective%20Newsroom%20has%20been%20established%20as%20an%20Indian%20company%2C%20wholly%20owned%20by%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20with%20four%20existing%20staff%20members%20leaving%20the%20BBC%20to%20lead%20Collective%20Newsroom.%20These%20senior%20leaders%20have%20a%20wealth%20of%20editorial%20and%20programme-making%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BBC%20will%20commission%20Collective%20Newsroom%20to%20produce%20its%20six%20Indian%20language%20services%20as%20well%20as%20Indian%20digital%20output%20and%20Indian%20YouTube%20channel%20in%20English%20for%20audiences%20globally%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAudiences%20in%20India%20can%20be%20assured%20that%20the%20BBC's%20Indian%20language%20services%20and%20unique%20range%20of%20quality%20output%20will%20inform%2C%20educate%20and%20entertain%20audiences%20across%20our%20diverse%20and%20highly%20engaged%20country%20under%20the%20agreement%20between%20the%20BBC%20and%20Collective%20Newsroom.%20We%20launch%20Collective%20Newsroom%20with%20big%20ambitions%20for%20audiences%20in%20India%20and%20beyond%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rupa%20Jha%2C%20Senior%20News%20Editor%2C%20BBC%20India%2C%20and%20founding%20shareholder%20of%20Collective%20Newsroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20said%20it%20has%20a%20long-held%20and%20deep-rooted%20place%20in%20India's%20media%20landscape%2C%20having%20first%20launched%20the%20Hindi%20language%20service%20in%201940.%20Since%20then%2C%20it%20has%20developed%20a%20range%20of%20BBC%20output%2C%20expanding%20the%20number%20of%20Indian%20language%20services%20and%20growing%20audience%20figures%20from%20%26quot%3Bdecade-to-decade%20with%20its%20agenda-setting%20and%20high%20impact%20journalism%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BBC's%20presence%20in%20India%20is%20steeped%20in%20a%20rich%20history%20that%20has%20always%20put%20audiences%20first%2C%20so%20we%20warmly%20welcome%20the%20formation%20of%20Collective%20Newsroom%20which%20continues%20that%20progression.%20The%20BBC%20will%20get%20first%20class%20content%20from%20Collective%20Newsroom%20that%20will%20be%20rooted%20in%20India%20and%20in%20line%20with%20the%20editorial%20standards%20audiences%20expect%20from%20the%20BBC%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jonathan%20Munro%2C%20Deputy%20CEO%2C%20BBC%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiliane%20Landor%2C%20Senior%20Controller%2C%20BBC%20News%20International%20Services%2C%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BTwo%20of%20the%20BBC's%20critical%20strengths%20are%20its%20truly%20global%20output%20for%20audiences%20and%20our%20reputation%20as%20a%20trusted%20source%20of%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20deeply%20committed%20to%20excellence%20in%20journalism%20for%20and%20from%20India%2C%20and%20this%20agreement%20ensures%20the%20continued%20production%20of%20independent%2C%20international%20and%20impartial%20journalism%20that%20the%20BBC%20News%20brand%20is%20renowned%20for%20in%20India%20and%20around%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%20Under%20the%20new%20arrangement%2C%20activity%20for%20BBC%20Monitoring%20and%20the%20BBC's%20English%20language%20newsgathering%20operation%20for%20global%20output%20will%20remain%20with%20the%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20content%20is%20provided%20in%20six%20languages%20-%20BBC%20News%20Hindi%2C%20BBC%20News%20Marathi%2C%20BBC%20News%20Gujarati%2C%