26quot%3Bstruggle%20will%20go%20on%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20Governor%20Karan%20Singh%20said%20the%20judgment%20did%20not%20mark%20the%20beginning%20of%20an%20era%2C%20as%20many%20are%20calling%20it%2C%20but%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20chapter%26quot%3B%20for%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20backed%20the%20Centre's%20move%20to%20scrap%20Article%20370%20saying%20the%20Article%2C%20declared%20temporary%20by%20the%20Constitution%2C%20was%20only%20meant%20to%20ease%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20integration%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20did%20not%20retain%20sovereignty%20when%20it%20joined%20India%20and%20its%20constituent%20assembly%20ceased%20to%20exist%20the%20moment%20it%20merged%20with%20India%2C%20added%20the%20five-judge%20constitution%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20should%20be%20put%20on%20par%20with%20other%20states%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20earliest%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20further%20said%2C%20ordering%20the%20Centre%20to%20hold%20elections%20by%20September%20next%20year%20and%20restore%20statehood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%20370%20was%20scrapped%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20split%20in%20August%202019%20%E2%80%93%20over%20a%20year%20after%20the%20PDP-BJP%20alliance%20government%20had%20collapsed%20.%20It%20took%20place%20while%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20was%20under%20President's%20Rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702400520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Faphsqams_farooq-abdullah_625x300_12_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-knows-it-may-come-back-in-200-years-farooq-abdullah-on-article-370-4661795%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Farooq%20Abdullah%2C%20the%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2