%20to%20the%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20jail%20authorities%20came%20to%20know%20about%20the%20dereliction%20of%20duty%2C%20they%20wrote%20to%20the%20Ludhiana%20police%20commissioner%20for%20action%20against%20the%20erring%20policemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELudhiana%20police%20commissioner%20Kuldeep%20Chahal%20said%20sub-inspector%20Mangal%20Singh%20and%20assistant%20sub-inspector%20Kuldeep%20Singh%2C%20who%20accompanied%20Lucky%20Sandhu%2C%20have%20been%20suspended.%20A%20departmental%20probe%20has%20also%20been%20ordered%20against%20them%2C%20said%20Chahal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702398960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F0uf34l98_lucky-sandhu-dancing_625x300_12_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpunjab-jail-inmate-taken-for-medical-checkup-seen-dancing-at-wedding-4661905%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20embarrassment%20to%20the%20Punjab%20Police%2C%20a%20jail%20inmate%20was%20seen%20dancing%20at%20a%20marriage%20ceremony%20after%20he%20was%20taken%20for%20a%20medical%20checkup%2C%20prompting%20authorities%20to%20suspend%20two%20police%20officers%20including%20a%20sub-inspector.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpunjab-jail-inmate-taken-for-medical-checkup-seen-dancing-at-wedding-4661905%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpunjab-jail-inmate-taken-for-medical-checkup-seen-dancing-at-wedding-4661905%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpunjab-jail-inmate-taken-for-medical-checkup-seen-dancing-at-wedding-4661905%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ITC%20to%20ramp%20up%20hotel%20room%