tement%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EESG%2C%20or%20environmental%2C%20social%20and%20governance%20parameters%20is%20used%20to%20screen%20investments%20based%20on%20corporate%20policies%20and%20to%20encourage%20companies%20to%20act%20responsibly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20will%20invest%20%24100%20billion%20in%20green%20energy%20transition%20over%2010%20years.%20The%20Adani%20portfolio%20businesses%20have%20active%20strategy%20to%20decarbonise%2C%20pledge%20to%20plant%20100%20million%20trees%20by%202030%2C%20and%20undertake%20innovative%20pilot%20projects%2C%20including%20development%20of%20hydrogen%20fuel%20cell%20electric%20truck%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20embarking%20on%20developing%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20ambitious%20green%20hydrogen%20ecosystems%20supported%20by%20a%20fully%20integrated%20value%20chain%20on%20the%20west%20coast%20of%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20roadmap%20to%20the%20net-zero%20transition%20will%20need%20last-mile%20green%20hydrogen%20solutions.%20To%20make%20green%20hydrogen%20adoption%20feasible%2C%20Adani's%20track%20record%20in%20large-scale%20renewables%20and%20fully%20integrated%20manufacturing%20with%20end-to-end%20EPC%20(engineering%2C%20procurement%20and%20construction)%20capabilities%20-%20all%20in%20a%20single%20location%20-%20uniquely%20positions%20it%20to%20lower%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F691898329%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-xzZ9GE6RjjCM4jlBKphA%5C%22%20data-auto-height%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20data-aspect-ratio%3D%5C%221.7790927021696252%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Adani%20Portfolio%20ESG%20H1FY24%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20striking%20advancements%20made%20by%20Adani%20portfolio%20companies%20on%20the%20ESG%20front%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdani%20Energy%20Solutions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Electricity%20Mumbai%2C%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20Adani%20Energy%20Solutions%2C%20has%20increased%20its%20renewable%20energy%20share%20in%20the%20overall%20mix%20to%20an%20impressive%2038.3%20per%20cent%2C%20positioning%20Mumbai%20as%20leading%20procurer%20of%20renewable%20energy%20(RE)%20amongst%20all%20megacities.%20This%20was%20made%20possible%20by%20the%20collaboration%20between%20portfolio%20companies%20Adani%20Energy%20Solutions%20(which%20owns%20the%20Mumbai%20distribution%20business)%20and%20Adani%20Green%20Energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdani%20Green%20Energy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Green%20Energy%20is%20the%20highest%20rated%20utility%20company%20in%20the%20world%20as%20per%20Sustainalytics.%20In%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20financial%20year%2C%20the%20renewable%20power%20company%20achieved%20zero%20waste%20to%20landfill%20for%20all%20operational%20sites%20and%20turned%20net%20water%20positive%20at%20all%20sites%20of%20200%20MW%20or%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdani%20Ports%20%26amp%3B%20SEZ%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Ports%2C%20which%20owns%2015%20ports%20and%20logistics%20business%2C%20is%20well%20on%20track%20to%20turn%20net-zero%20by%202040.%20In%20the%20first%20half%20of%20FY24%2C%20it%20achieved%20a%2015%20per%20cent%20share%20of%20renewables%20in%20the%20total%20energy%20mix%2C%20reduced%20energy%20intensity%20by%2046%20per%20cent%2C%20energy%20emission%20by%2048%20per%20cent%2C%20and%20water%20consumption%20intensity%20by%2059%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdani%20Enterprises%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Enterprises%20is%20building%20three%20giga-factories%20with%20a%20target%20to%20develop%2010%20GW%20solar%20panels%2C%2010%20GW%20wind%20turbines%2C%20and%205%20GW%20hydrogen%20electrolysers%20as%20part%20of%20its%20low-cost%20integrated%20green%20hydrogen%20project.%20For%20solar%20module%20manufacturing%2C%20the%20glass%20factory%20is%20completed%2C%20with%20work%20commencing%20on%20the%20ingot%20and%20wafer%20plant.%20In%20October%2C%20the%20company%20started%20production%20of%20India's%20largest%20wind%20turbine%20of%205.2%20MW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EESG%20Innovations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProactive%20experimentation%20with%20green%20hydrogen-based%20decarbonisation%20solutions%20are%20being%20conducted%20in%20anticipation%20of%20wider%20adoption%20as%20costs%20come%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20promote%20reduced%20emission%20and%20sustainable%20energy%2C%20Adani%20Power%20partnered%20with%20IHI%20Corporation%20and%20Kowa%20company%20to%20explore%20ammonia%20co-firing%20at%20the%20Adani%20Power%20Mundra%20plant.%20The%20studies%20aim%20at%20initially%20de-carbonising%20Adani's%20coal-fired%20plants%2C%20but%20with%20a%20larger%20objective%20to%20implement%20the%20technology%20in%20other%20coal-fired%20plants%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20significant%20move%2C%20Adani%20Enterprises%20entered%20into%20an%20agreement%20with%20Ashok%20Leyland%20and%20Ballard%20Power%20to%20develop%20a%20hydrogen%20fuel%20cell%20electric%20truck%20(FCET)%20for%20mining%20logistics%20and%20transportation%2C%20which%20will%20be%20Asia's%20first%20and%20one%20of%20the%20few%20companies%20globally%20to%20operate%20green%20hydrogen-powered%20mining%20trucks.%20The%20launch%20of%20the%20FCET%20in%20India%20is%20scheduled%20for%202023%2C%20marking%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20advancing%20a%20hydrogen%20economy%20and%20positioning%20India%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20emerging%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20further%20support%20decarbonisation%2C%20the%20Adani%20portfolio%20has%20pledged%20to%20plant%20100%20million%20trees%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Co