0says%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330342%2Ftamil-nadu-madhya-pradesh-policies-for-inclusive-education-improve-early-childhood-care-sonali-saini-sols-arc%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecuriosity%20and%20willingness%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20look%20beyond%20the%20textbook%20stood%20him%20in%20good%20stead.%20He%20cites%20one%20such%20instance%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Physics%2C%20there%20is%20a%20concept%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Theory%20of%20Relativity%E2%80%99.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20in%20the%20Class%2011%20syllabus%20which%20I%20was%20studying%20at%20the%20time%2C%20but%20regardless%20of%20it%2C%20I%20studied%20it.%20I%20also%20ended%20up%20deriving%20the%20equation%20for%20the%20equivalence%20of%20electric%20and%20magnetic%20fields.%20I%20did%20it%20purely%20out%20of%20interest.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20you%20can%20only%20imagine%20Kalpit%E2%80%99s%20astonishment%20when%20one%20of%20the%20questions%20in%20the%20JEE%20Mains%20was%20on%20this%20theory.%20He%20smiled%20to%20himself%20as%20he%20went%20on%20to%20derive%20the%20equation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20attitude%20to%20learn%20coupled%20with%20an%20enthusiasm%20for%20the%20subjects%20has%20been%20Kalpit%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330277%2Fbengaluru-startup-stemonsters-founder-dr-sonali-dasgupta-making-science-fun-for-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edriving%20force%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20credits%20this%20duo%20with%20keeping%20him%20determined%20throughout%20the%20JEE%20prep%20journey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMy%20life's%20journey%20so%20far%3A%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%E2%80%93%20Was%20interested%20in%20studies%20from%20a%20young%20age%2C%20had%20fun%20but%20also%20had%20curiosity%20in%20learning.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%E2%80%93%2